1248
01:11:13,000 --> 01:11:15,000
[SPEAKER_02] Da si možda, da imaš krivi ulet.

1249
01:11:15,000 --> 01:11:16,000
[SPEAKER_02] To je bar u mene bilo ono.

1250
01:11:16,000 --> 01:11:18,000
[SPEAKER_02] Da imam krivu ulet, krivu priču,

1251
01:11:18,000 --> 01:11:20,000
[SPEAKER_02] da imam krivu namjeru.

1252
01:11:20,000 --> 01:11:22,000
[SPEAKER_02] Žene to osjete.

1253
01:11:22,000 --> 01:11:24,000
