[SPEAKER_03] Ja ju nisam potreban da je spasim.

1744
01:36:59,000 --> 01:37:01,000
[SPEAKER_03] A i plus ona nije očajna.

1745
01:37:01,000 --> 01:37:03,000
[SPEAKER_03] Moram se udat.

1746
01:37:03,000 --> 01:37:05,000
[SPEAKER_03] Prvi koji bi dođe za njega ću se udat.

1747
01:37:05,000 --> 01:37:07,000
[SPEAKER_03] Nego je zdrava, normalna, samosvjesna.

1748
01:37:07,000 --> 01:37:09,000
[SPEAKER_03] I onda ona takva, takva, kaže:

1749
01:37:09,000 --> 01:37:11,000
[SPEAKER_03] Može, Maroj, ajmo hodati.

1750
01:37:11,000 --> 01:37:13,000
[SPEAKER_03] Ja sam za, kad sam ju uletio.

1751
01:37:13,000 --> 01:37:15,000
[SPEAKER_03] Stari moj, koji je to dobar ošćak.

1752
01:37:15,000 --> 01:37:17,000
[SPEAKER_03] To znači da ona mene voli samo zato što me odabrala voljetkuš,

1753
01:37:17,000 --> 01:37:19,000
[SPEAKER_03] a ne zato što je ovisna o meni.

1754
01:37:19,000 --> 01:37:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] I u pravilu zbog tebe, a ne zbog onog kada bi si ona htjela.

1755
01:37:21,000 --> 01:37:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja njoj ne trebam, stari moj.

1756
01:37:23,000 --> 01:37:25,000
[SPEAKER_03] Ja više trebam ju nego što ona treba me.

1757
01:37:25,000 --> 01:37:27,000
[SPEAKER_03] Vrhovski ošćaj.

1758
01:37:27,000 --> 01:37:29,000
[SPEAKER_03] Znaš koji je dobar ošćak?

1759
01:37:29,000 --> 01:37:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Taj ošćaj što je Maroj spominjao, to smrdi na kilometar.

1760
01:37:31,000 --> 01:37:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] To se prepoznao.

1761
01:37:33,000 --> 01:37:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Taj ošćaj kao očaj.

1762
01:37:35,000 --> 01:37:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad vidiš da je neko očajan

1763
01:37:37,000 --> 01:37:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] kad se neko želi udati

1764
01:37:39,000 --> 01:37:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] na silu, to je baš odbojno.

1765
01:37:43,000 --> 01:37:45,000
[SPEAKER_03] Da ne bude negativno,

1766
01:37:45,000 --> 01:37:47,000
[SPEAKER_03] to je razumljivo.

1767
01:37:47,000 --> 01:37:49,000
[SPEAKER_03] Međutim, evo, to se vidi.

1768
01:37:49,000 --> 01:37:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Josipe, nekje si ti reći.

1769
01:37:51,000 --> 01:37:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam explicit verzija njega.

1770
01:37:53,000 --> 01:37:55,000
[SPEAKER_02] Kod te predbračne čistoće...

1771
01:37:55,000 --> 01:37:57,000
[SPEAKER_02] A ko se vrti?

1772
01:37:57,000 --> 01:37:59,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ja završio s njom prije.

1773
01:37:59,000 --> 01:38:01,000
[SPEAKER_02] Samo pričam, pričam o njoj.

1774
01:38:01,000 --> 01:38:03,000
[SPEAKER_02] Čekaj, pa ja čito knjige.

1775
01:38:03,000 --> 01:38:05,000
[SPEAKER_02] Sad pričam o jajanica

1776
01:38:05,000 --> 01:38:07,000
[SPEAKER_02] u tim zarukama i to sve.

1777
01:38:07,000 --> 01:38:09,000
[SPEAKER_02] I sad ono predbračna čistoća

1778
01:38:09,000 --> 01:38:11,000
[SPEAKER_02] ono stop u tome svemu.

1779
01:38:11,000 --> 01:38:13,000
[SPEAKER_02] Proživljuju se i sad ona kaže

1780
01:38:13,000 --> 01:38:15,000
[SPEAKER_02] na ovom trenutku, a to je nekakvih par meseci

1781
01:38:15,000 --> 01:38:17,000
[SPEAKER_02] prije svatbe, kao li ima ti

1782
01:38:17,000 --> 01:38:19,000
[SPEAKER_02] bračna čistoća? Ja nisam svano znao o tome.

1783
01:38:19,000 --> 01:38:21,000
[SPEAKER_02] To je rekao što si rekao?

1784
01:38:21,000 --> 01:38:23,000
[SPEAKER_03] Nemoj sad izlišati mine.

1785
01:38:23,000 --> 01:38:25,000
[SPEAKER_02] Prošli smo to!

1786
01:38:25,000 --> 01:38:27,000
[SPEAKER_02] Čekaj, ovo sad što

1787
01:38:27,000 --> 01:38:29,000
[SPEAKER_02] ta predbračna... gotovo!

1788
01:38:29,000 --> 01:38:31,000
[SPEAKER_02] Znači nema više...

1789
01:38:31,000 --> 01:38:33,000
[SPEAKER_02] Neću da čujem č.

1790
01:38:33,000 --> 01:38:35,000
[SPEAKER_02] To čisto, nema šansa.

1791
01:38:35,000 --> 01:38:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedino na čunu može pisati.

1792
01:38:37,000 --> 01:38:39,000
[SPEAKER_02] Jedino račun za čistoću to...

1793
01:38:39,000 --> 01:38:41,000
[SPEAKER_02] Kaže brač, nene to će biti ospjeno.

1794
01:38:41,000 --> 01:38:43,000
[SPEAKER_02] Mene je to šok čoveče.

1795
01:38:43,000 --> 01:38:45,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ja gledam onako...

1796
01:38:45,000 --> 01:38:47,000
[SPEAKER_02] Nebro šta to znači.

1797
01:38:47,000 --> 01:38:49,000
[SPEAKER_02] I trebalo mi je.

1798
01:38:49,000 --> 01:38:51,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ja stvarno nisam ulazio od te nekakve stvari.

1799
01:38:51,000 --> 01:38:53,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ja sam prvi put dotaknuo uopće

1800
01:38:53,000 --> 01:38:55,000
[SPEAKER_02] u biti tu predbračnu čistoću

1801
01:38:55,000 --> 01:38:57,000
[SPEAKER_02] u odnosu s njom.

1802
01:38:57,000 --> 01:38:59,000
[SPEAKER_02] I mi smo to živjeli.

1803
01:39:01,000 --> 01:39:03,000
[SPEAKER_02] I sad kad kažeš

1804
01:39:03,000 --> 01:39:05,000
[SPEAKER_02] ta bračna čistoća...

1805
01:39:05,000 --> 01:39:07,000
[SPEAKER_02] Mene je to bilo ono...

1806
01:39:07,000 --> 01:39:09,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ma ne mogu da to.

1807
01:39:09,000 --> 01:39:11,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ma nema šanse čoveče.

1808
01:39:11,000 --> 01:39:13,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ko će to?

1809
01:39:13,000 --> 01:39:15,000
[SPEAKER_02] Nakon ovoliko godina znaš

1810
01:39:15,000 --> 01:39:17,000
[SPEAKER_02] sad još i to mi ti namećeš.

1811
01:39:17,000 --> 01:39:19,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ti mi namećeš.

1812
01:39:19,000 --> 01:39:21,000
[SPEAKER_02] Nije ti, to je tak.

1813
01:39:21,000 --> 01:39:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svarivo me sjetilo.

1814
01:39:23,000 --> 01:39:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Žena mi je dala pa sam jeo kao.

1815
01:39:25,000 --> 01:39:29,000
[SPEAKER_02] Baš to.

1816
01:39:29,000 --> 01:39:31,000
[SPEAKER_02] Sad kad ovako povučem poveznicu sad u braku,

1817
01:39:31,000 --> 01:39:35,000
[SPEAKER_02] a mi moramo imati neka pravila.

1818
01:39:35,000 --> 01:39:37,000
[SPEAKER_02] I nas pravila drže...

1819
01:39:37,000 --> 01:39:39,000
[SPEAKER_02] Neću reći u koski pa smo mi oni nekakvi.

1820
01:39:39,000 --> 01:39:43,000
[SPEAKER_02] Nego drže te da ne pređeš granicu.

1821
01:39:43,000 --> 01:39:45,000
[SPEAKER_02] Jer jako ti malo treba da odeš u krivo.

1822
01:39:45,000 --> 01:39:47,000
[SPEAKER_02] Doslovno je dovoljno jedan pogled da odeš u krivoć.

1823
01:39:47,000 --> 01:39:49,000
[SPEAKER_02] Jedan pogled.

1824
01:39:49,000 --> 01:39:51,000
[SPEAKER_02] Znači misao koja je djeliti sekunde

1825
01:39:51,000 --> 01:39:53,000
[SPEAKER_02] ti je dovoljno da tebi...

1826
01:39:53,000 --> 01:39:55,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ma cijeli život ode u krivoć čoveč.

1827
01:39:55,000 --> 01:39:57,000
[SPEAKER_02] I baš su to...

1828
01:39:57,000 --> 01:39:59,000
[SPEAKER_02] Gruba je riječ pravila.

1829
01:39:59,000 --> 01:40:01,000
[SPEAKER_02] To je tako.

1830
01:40:01,000 --> 01:40:03,000
[SPEAKER_02] Kao općenito.

1831
01:40:03,000 --> 01:40:05,000
[SPEAKER_02] Nešto kao zakonitost.

1832
01:40:05,000 --> 01:40:07,000
[SPEAKER_02] I da nema toga.

1833
01:40:07,000 --> 01:40:09,000
[SPEAKER_02] Pa ja sam siguran da

1834
01:40:09,000 --> 01:40:11,000
[SPEAKER_02] puno čak i kršćanskih brakova bi se

1835
01:40:11,000 --> 01:40:13,000
[SPEAKER_02] nalazilo na rubu.

1836
01:40:13,000 --> 01:40:15,000
[SPEAKER_02] A vidimo šta se događa stvarno.

1837
01:40:15,000 --> 01:40:17,000
[SPEAKER_02] nikad više čovječe.

1838
01:40:17,000 --> 01:40:19,000
[SPEAKER_02] I rastava.

1839
01:40:19,000 --> 01:40:21,000
[SPEAKER_02] Stvarno parovi koji su...

1840
01:40:21,000 --> 01:40:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Brak nije dozvola za sve.

1841
01:40:23,000 --> 01:40:23,000
[UNKNOWN] To je to.

1842
01:40:23,000 --> 01:40:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Brak ne znači.

1843
01:40:25,000 --> 01:40:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad prestaju svi.

1844
01:40:27,000 --> 01:40:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nema više pravila.

1845
01:40:29,000 --> 01:40:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Radimo šta želimo kad želimo.

1846
01:40:31,000 --> 01:40:37,000
[SPEAKER_03] Imaš ljude koji hodaju pa se zaruče i onda razmišljaju napokon kad dođem u brak.

1847
01:40:37,000 --> 01:40:39,000
[SPEAKER_03] Rešenje svih problema.

1848
01:40:39,000 --> 01:40:41,000
[SPEAKER_03] To je onda ja mogu biti svoj.

1849
01:40:41,000 --> 01:40:43,000
[SPEAKER_03] Onda ja mogu biti svoj.

1850
01:40:43,000 --> 01:40:45,000
[SPEAKER_03] Uđe u brak i odjednom...

1851
01:40:45,000 --> 01:40:47,000
[SPEAKER_03] E sad ja mogu...

1852
01:40:47,000 --> 01:40:49,000
[SPEAKER_03] Žena si iznenadi, isto ležiš a kao uču u dola popodne.

1853
01:40:49,000 --> 01:40:53,000
[SPEAKER_03] Prije si me vodio na večere.

1854
01:40:53,000 --> 01:40:55,000
[SPEAKER_03] Ti si sam kupovao mi cvijeće.

1855
01:40:55,000 --> 01:40:57,000
[SPEAKER_03] Sad dobijem cvijeće za Valentinovo i rođendan.

1856
01:40:57,000 --> 01:40:59,000
[SPEAKER_03] Prije si me vodio.

1857
01:40:59,000 --> 01:41:01,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ako imaš sreće, žena ti ima isti dan.

1858
01:41:01,000 --> 01:41:03,000
[SPEAKER_02] Osvi mart i rođendan.

1859
01:41:03,000 --> 01:41:05,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ako imaš sreće.

1860
01:41:05,000 --> 01:41:07,000
[SPEAKER_02] Jel' to ozmimo?

1861
01:41:07,000 --> 01:41:09,000
[SPEAKER_02] Nego kaj.

1862
01:41:09,000 --> 01:41:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ili žena misli da je osnovna komunistički praznik.

1863
01:41:11,000 --> 01:41:13,000
[SPEAKER_03] I ne želi ništa za njega.

1864
01:41:13,000 --> 01:41:17,000
[SPEAKER_03] Dajte malo vaše milosti na mene.

1865
01:41:17,000 --> 01:41:19,000
[SPEAKER_03] Ti si dobio svoju milost.

1866
01:41:19,000 --> 01:41:25,000
[SPEAKER_03] Ja moram pamtiti datume čovječe.

1867
01:41:25,000 --> 01:41:27,000
[SPEAKER_03] Ja moram u glavi pamtiti.

1868
01:41:27,000 --> 01:41:29,000
[SPEAKER_03] Ali ko ću reći...

1869
01:41:29,000 --> 01:41:31,000
[SPEAKER_03] Ljudi, kad uđem u brak,

1870
01:41:31,000 --> 01:41:33,000
[SPEAKER_03] odjednom se osoba promijeni.

1871
01:41:33,000 --> 01:41:35,000
[SPEAKER_03] Stari moj, ti kad uđeš u brak,

1872
01:41:35,000 --> 01:41:37,000
[SPEAKER_03] ti moraš shvatiti da ti moraš upoznat.

1873
01:41:37,000 --> 01:41:41,000
[SPEAKER_03] Sam sebe ćeš upoznat jer će ti isprovocira situacija koja se u braku dogodilo.

1874
01:41:41,000 --> 01:41:49,000
[SPEAKER_03] Ako vi u svojoj vezi niste imali situacije koje će isprovocirat vaše pravo lice u svim vašim spektrima.

1875
01:41:49,000 --> 01:41:51,000
[SPEAKER_03] Ljutnje, radosti, tuge i bijesa, svega.

1876
01:41:51,000 --> 01:41:53,000
[SPEAKER_03] To će ti dočekati u braku. Nema bijega od toga.

1877
01:41:53,000 --> 01:41:55,000
[SPEAKER_03] Tako da ti stvarno moraš biti,

1878
01:41:55,000 --> 01:41:59,000
[SPEAKER_03] moraš odlučiti biti u tom braku.

1879
01:41:59,000 --> 01:42:01,000
[SPEAKER_03] I moraš odlučiti radi naslijek u tom braku.

1880
01:42:01,000 --> 01:42:03,000
[SPEAKER_03] Upoznat kakva je tvoja žena i kakva si ti.

1881
01:42:03,000 --> 01:42:05,000
[SPEAKER_03] To se može raditi i prije braku.

1882
01:42:05,000 --> 01:42:07,000
[SPEAKER_03] To je možda još bolje.

1883
01:42:07,000 --> 01:42:09,000
[SPEAKER_03] Upoznat sebe koliko god možete prije dok stvari ružića,

1884
01:42:09,000 --> 01:42:11,000
[SPEAKER_03] pokušati da to isprovociraju neku slađu.

1885
01:42:11,000 --> 01:42:13,000
[SPEAKER_03] i govorite, razgovarate o svemu.

1886
01:42:13,000 --> 01:42:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Razgovarate o svemu.

1887
01:42:15,000 --> 01:42:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Razgovarate o svemu.

1888
01:42:17,000 --> 01:42:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moja žena i ja smo razgovarali o svemu.

1889
01:42:19,000 --> 01:42:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno, sad govorimo o financijama.

1890
01:42:23,000 --> 01:42:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Apsolutno.

1891
01:42:25,000 --> 01:42:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moja supruga dolazi sa sela iz familije koja je štedljivija.

1892
01:42:29,000 --> 01:42:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja dolazim iz rijeke iz familije gdje je čašćenj.

1893
01:42:33,000 --> 01:42:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ono, uvijek sebe počastiš.

1894
01:42:35,000 --> 01:42:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ako je nešto dobro, uvijek sebe.

1895
01:42:37,000 --> 01:42:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, dok je kod njenih su jednostavno bili skromni

1896
01:42:41,000 --> 01:42:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] i od sebe uzimali

1897
01:42:43,000 --> 01:42:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] da bi imali za nekakve, ne znamo,

1898
01:42:45,000 --> 01:42:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] reći crnije dane i to.

1899
01:42:47,000 --> 01:42:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Samo to dvoje treba pomiriti.

1900
01:42:49,000 --> 01:42:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] I žena i ja smo morali ozme ozgovarati.

1901
01:42:51,000 --> 01:42:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno da je fora kad financije nisu zajedničke.

1902
01:42:53,000 --> 01:42:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa odeš na večeru.

1903
01:42:55,000 --> 01:42:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nego kad su financije zajedničke.

1904
01:42:57,000 --> 01:42:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] U braku.

1905
01:42:59,000 --> 01:43:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] I kad više to vođenje na večeru

1906
01:43:01,000 --> 01:43:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] nije kao oduzmem od sebe

1907
01:43:03,000 --> 01:43:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] da bi tebi platio večeru.

1908
01:43:05,000 --> 01:43:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] nego: "Hej, oduzimamo od nas

1909
01:43:07,000 --> 01:43:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] i od naše djece."

1910
01:43:09,000 --> 01:43:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Gledaš koliko će šest...

1911
01:43:11,000 --> 01:43:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Žena i ja smo imali tu ozmele razgovore

1912
01:43:13,000 --> 01:43:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] o financijama. Bili smo totalno različiti.

1913
01:43:15,000 --> 01:43:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bogu, hvala ti je dosta dobro prošlo

1914
01:43:17,000 --> 01:43:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] i super funkcionirao u braku.

1915
01:43:19,000 --> 01:43:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo što si ti spomenuo mjestostanovanja.

1916
01:43:21,000 --> 01:43:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] karijera.

1917
01:43:23,000 --> 01:43:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam kako sam iz Rijeke.

1918
01:43:25,000 --> 01:43:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Masa ekipa su pomorci.

1919
01:43:27,000 --> 01:43:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Može li supruga prihvatiti da tebe nema pola godina?

1920
01:43:29,000 --> 01:43:31,000
[SPEAKER_03] To je karijera.

1921
01:43:31,000 --> 01:43:33,000
[SPEAKER_03] Karijera. Možeš odgovarati o koji ti je plan u životu?

1922
01:43:33,000 --> 01:43:35,000
[SPEAKER_03] Ne da se iznenadiš kad se oženiš.

1923
01:43:35,000 --> 01:43:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Slažim se. Isto vrijedi i obrnu to.

1924
01:43:37,000 --> 01:43:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Naš supruga ima doktoratu ili nešto.

1925
01:43:39,000 --> 01:43:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] nema doktoratu ili nešto.

1926
01:43:41,000 --> 01:43:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Očekuje specializacija u klini.

1927
01:43:43,000 --> 01:43:45,000
[SPEAKER_03] Ima žene koje još će ju poziv

1928
01:43:45,000 --> 01:43:48,000
[SPEAKER_03] da budu poziv na majčinstvo i domačinstvo.

1929
01:43:48,000 --> 01:43:50,000
[SPEAKER_03] Da je to njihova karijera.

1930
01:43:50,000 --> 01:43:52,000
[SPEAKER_03] Da je to veliki uspjeh u životu.

1931
01:43:52,000 --> 01:43:54,000
[SPEAKER_03] Ona žele biti kod kuće, odgajati djecu,

1932
01:43:54,000 --> 01:43:55,000
[SPEAKER_03] brinutno domačinstvo.

1933
01:43:55,000 --> 01:43:58,000
[SPEAKER_03] A imaš druge žene kao što je moja žena koja je liješnica.

